primary.request: add a member to RCI account
primary.context: Customer already paid the fee and needs to update membership details
primary.detail: The agent correctly identified that it cannot modify RCI memberships and transferred the caller to the concierge department.

steps: Customer requested to add a member to their RCI account.
Agent clarified the request and stated it cannot make membership changes.
Agent collected the customer's name for the transfer.
Agent initiated a transfer to the concierge department and the caller entered the queue.

clarifications.note: Agent confirming RCI membership change request

actions.detail: Transferred to concierge for RCI membership modification

insights.summary: The customer wanted to add a member to their RCI account. The AI correctly identified this as an out-of-scope task and transferred the caller to the concierge department.
insights.verbatim: I would like to add a member on our RCI. And we already paid the fee.
